      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its signature individual throttle bodies. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers, providing the communicative feedback and high-limit handling these cars are known for. While the aesthetics show minor road-derived character consistent with a well-loved driver, the drivetrain remains potent and the steering rack is tight. A well-sorted analog machine ready for the twisties.",
